OL,3,CWhat can we all do to protect our
OL,4,Cmoney and plan for the future?
OL,6,FReporter Ruth Dodsworth speaks of her
OL,7,Fpersonal experience of economic abuse,
OL,8,Fand the long term financial
OL,9,Fimplications.
OL,11,FRuth continues to share her story
OL,12,Fpublicly to try to help others,
OL,13,Frecently receiving an OBE for her
OL,14,Ftireless work helping victims and
OL,15,Fsurvivors of domestic abuse. She is
OL,16,Falso an ambassador of a charity called
OL,17,FSurviving Economic Abuse. Their latest
OL,18,Freport revealed that 55% of women in
OL,19,Fthe UK aren't aware of economic abuse.
