OL,3,CWhat can we all do to protect our
OL,4,Cmoney and plan for the future?
OL,6,FTonight hears from Teresa J Payne and
OL,7,FSimon Steele-Williams from legal firm
OL,8,FParfitt Cresswell. They reveal how
OL,9,Fthey uncovered a sophisticated scam
OL,10,Finvolving faked wills, forged
OL,11,Fsignatures, and fraudulent
OL,12,Fapplications for probate. Exploiting a
OL,13,Fgovernment-published list of unclaimed
OL,14,Festates, fraudsters are believed to
OL,15,Fhave obtained legal control of assets
OL,16,Fthey have no rightful claim to,
OL,17,Fcashing in hundreds of thousands of
OL,18,Fpounds before families even realised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
