OL,3,CWhat can we all do to protect our
OL,4,Cmoney and plan for the future?
OL,6,FSimon Steele-Williams told Tonight:
OL,7,F"Although we moved very quickly, they
OL,8,Fmanaged to spirit away very
OL,9,Fsubstantial sums of money which we've
OL,10,Fnot been able to recover. There are
OL,11,Fnow into double figure cases emerging
OL,12,Fand I have to be honest, I think it's
OL,13,Fthe tip of the iceberg."
