OL,3,CWhat can we all do to protect our
OL,4,Cmoney and plan for the future?
OL,6,F"We've had to go through the court
OL,7,Fprocess, which we're currently still
OL,8,Fgoing through. Emotionally it's very
OL,9,Fhard because it's finding that money
OL,10,Fevery month that you get the
OL,11,Fsolicitor's bill. I've had to spend
OL,12,Fover 11,000 pounds and yet we're still
OL,13,Fnot at the conclusion, so we don't
OL,14,Fknow how much it's going to continue
OL,15,Fto cost us. It's also been quite
OL,16,Ffrightening. Because we don't know who
OL,17,Fthese people are. You worry all the
OL,18,Ftime, you just think. How safe am I?"
